      <simple-id uuid='{97A3BF3B-1642-4203-87F5-D695EF9BA5D9}' />
      <desc>An interactive Tableau dashboard developed to analyze cloud service usage, cost distribution, and resource consumption. It visualizes key insights such as total cloud spending, monthly cost trends, service usage patterns, regional cost analysis, and customer segmentation to support better cloud resource management and cost optimization.
</desc>
